thread.title: Ashley Shepard

author: Ashley Shepard
title: Ashley Shepard
text: Ordered 2 boxes per eye, entered the info given to me by my eye doctor and sent in the picture of the script. Received an email that this was not a proper prescription. They notified my doctor and got it fixed for me in 1-2 days. Total time until order received after order placed including delays was around 1.5 wks. Very satisfied, will order all my contacts from here.
